     :EndIf
     (name args)‚ÜêNormalize action                                       ‚çù Separate action name from its arguments and standardize structure
     name‚Üêobjref Canonize name                                          ‚çù In cases where capitalization is optional, adjust it to standard
     :If ‚éïNULL‚â¢result‚Üêobjref(name Immediate)args ‚ãÑ :Return ‚ãÑ :EndIf     ‚çù Perform any out-of-band "instant" processing
